txt.en: Nud-heden will never be recovered until the grodbog-queen is struck down.
While the grodbog-queen still lives, dwarves will never reclaim their honourable home of old. She must be struck down. Only then will this place be left in peace.

The grodbog-queen in Nud-heden is laying eggs and nurturing larvae. She is creating a swarm to protect herself, while she continues to breed unharmed.\n\nYou should defeat the grodbog-queen in Nud-heden.

Nud-heden now has a chance to be claimed by something other than gredbyg. Will dwarves once again call this home?\n\nKhazad-d√ªm will not be restored to glory all at once, but stone-by-stone, it will shine once more.
